## AI Context Directory Addition

### Purpose
Added .ai/ directory that was already created but not yet committed. This directory enables quick AI assistant onboarding with project context.

### Files Added
- **context-eval.json**: Q&A pairs to validate AI understanding of the project
- **generate_resurrection_prompt.sh**: Script to generate standardized context prompt
- **project-context.md**: Human-readable project overview

### Relation to Issues
- Created issue #4 to track this feature
- Closed immediately as already implemented
- Now properly committed to version control

### Benefits
- Faster AI onboarding for new sessions
- Consistent project context across AI interactions
- Validation mechanism for AI understanding
- Self-documenting project structure
